{"word":"G2547 - κἀκεῖθεν - kakeîthen - kak-i'-then - And afterward","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κἀκεῖθεν</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">kakeîthen</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">kak-i'-then</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">And afterward</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"அவ்விடம் விட்டு, அதுமுதல் - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"from that place, afterwards, thence also"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2532 - καί - kaí - kahee/2532\">G2532</a> and <a href=\"#/G1564 - ἐκεῖθεν - ekeîthen - ek-i'-then/1564\">G1564</a>; <i>likewise from that place</i> (or <i>time</i>): - and afterward (from) (thence), thence also.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}